  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA13">
<l>takavuṭaiyār tāmuḷarē ṟārakalañ cārap</l>
<l>pukaviṭutal pollātu kaṇṭīr - mikavaṭara</l>
<l>vūrntiṭumā nāka morunāṇ malaimakaḷaic</l>
<l>cārntiṭumē lēpāvan tāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If he possesses fitness, it would be bad to let it enter</l>
<l>so as to approach [his] garlanded chest, see, the big snake</l>
<l>that mounts [him?], very tightly compressed, if one day it were to approach</l>
<l>the daughter of the mountain, that would be evil.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
